OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fslowly ease to leave clear skies and a
OL,7,Fchilly evening for many. Overnight,
OL,8,Frain pushes in from the west with some
OL,9,Fhill snow in Scotland. Temperatures
OL,10,Fwill fall below freezing in the east,
OL,11,Fbringing a patchy frost here.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FSunny spells to start in the
OL,14,Feast on Sunday. Rain will continue to
OL,15,Fspread eastwards, soon clearing to
OL,16,Fsunny spells and showers, heavy at
OL,17,Ftimes. Coastal gales in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
